cc:Work.dc:description:
Dispenser for stackable (flat) items of same size
Set *bottomheight* to 0 for a wall mounting variant. Please add mounting holes yourself.
Created with Boxes.py (https://boxes.hackerspace-bamberg.de/) Command line: boxes Dispenser Command line short: boxes Dispenser
